'''夏威夷會議中心'''（{{lang-en|Hawaii Convention Center}}）位於[[美國|美國]][[夏威夷|夏威夷]][[檀香山|檀香山]]的一個[[展覽中心|展覽中心]]。

2011年，[[亞洲太平洋經濟合作組織|亞洲太平洋經濟合作組織]]（APEC）於夏威夷會議中心舉行峰會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eastwestcenter.org/news-center/news-releases/hawaii-to-host-apec-summit-in-2011/ |title=Hawaii to Host APEC Summit in 2011 |work=East-West Center |date= |accessdate=2015-10-01 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923233154/http://www.eastwestcenter.org/news-center/news-releases/hawaii-to-host-apec-summit-in-2011/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，2015年上映的電影《[[侏羅紀世界|侏羅紀世界]]》曾到此取景拍攝<ref>{{cite web |url= http://m.theepochtimes.com/n3/646885-jurassic-world-jurassic-park-4-new-hawaii-set-photos-details-about-possible-sequels/ |title= Jurassic World (Jurassic Park 4): New Hawaii Set Photos, Details About Possible Sequels |newspaper= The Epoch Times |date= 2014-04-28 |accessdate= 2015-10-01 |first= Zachary |last= Stieber |archive-date= 2014-11-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141108090016/http://m.theepochtimes.com/n3/646885-jurassic-world-jurassic-park-4-new-hawaii-set-photos-details-about-possible-sequels/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

